The paper is about data augmentation techniques for training deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also uses reinforcement learning and optimization techniques, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the use of data augmentation in natural language processing (NLP) tasks, which falls under computational linguistics (cs.CL).
